{"tid":1183890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜：希望學習鄧小平 讓人民「發大財」","createTime":"2019-06-03T09:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T13:57:31.000Z","uid":144372,"like":6,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c7f2860f1b503f24e2b0881baac62ae79fc671","tid":1183890,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190602/20693568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693568&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=09d349fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693568&h=3338d0a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190602/20693568</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜之後火力全開，將民進黨罵成一文不值，只懂玩權鬥：由民進黨黨員擔任中選會主委、容許監察院彈劾檢察官、人民感受不到經濟成果。他斥對外只不斷灑錢，但又不斷失去邦交國，屬「凱子外交」，處理兩岸關係只「帶領台灣人碰撞兩岸」。他承諾總統最重要工作就是國防、外交、兩岸，透露「如果我有機會承擔這樣責任」，國防可保證任何情況下對方不敢輕啟戰端，外交可搞好友邦關係，全部肩負經濟任務，變成「發財外交」，對外可簽訂FTA（自由貿易協定）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>他又希望學習中共已故領導人鄧小平，做到確定國家發展總目標「台灣安全、人民有錢」</strong>、不貪不取、善用人才及有同理心四大目標，令「未來台灣競爭力會一飛沖天」。"},{"pid":"3576cbe5996f0d962edc87ffb467962b7ba1bdeb","tid":1183890,"uid":41545,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"好講唔講講佢 咁台仔幾蠢都知你會出坦克掛？"},{"pid":"2d50657928bf4c56bccfb914d934f3b8e09f0f2a","tid":1183890,"uid":144372,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"3576cbe5996f0d962edc87ffb467962b7ba1bdeb","tid":1183890,"uid":41545,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"好講唔講講佢 咁台仔幾蠢都知你會出坦克掛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"韓生：總之發到財乜都得"},{"pid":"47b6e55b73c97ea98795e7798799ca4b51477b24","tid":1183890,"uid":29620,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:33:37.000Z","msg"